div.div: To defeat his uncle who destroyed his family, the teenager Xuan Tian embarked on a martial arts training journey to hone his sword techniques. From a teenager who knew nothing to a Sword God of his generation, those he once saw as strong are now mere specks of dust to him. With one finger, I obliterate all; With my sword, I defy the heavens! And his path, leads him directly to the limitless heavens!

The Wanjie Continent is filled with prodigies, acclaimed as deities, princes, and taoists, representing the future of each sect. The untalented and ordinary Qin Shu was supposed to one of these prodigies due to his father, one of the strongest men on the continent. But instead he was looked down and jeered upon by everyone in his sect. Until one day, his Wanjie Checkin System finally reached 100%, and all of a sudden he reached peak power by unlocking the skill of Perpetual Dantian!
(Source: Tencent, translated)
